{"id":41719,"date":"2025-02-18T13:47:50","date_gmt":"2025-02-18T13:47:50","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/search-recovery.com\/abbingtonhouse\/services\/medically-supervised-detox\/"},"modified":"2025-04-30T09:05:18","modified_gmt":"2025-04-30T09:05:18","slug":"medically-supervised-detox","status":"publish","type":"residential-rehab","link":"https:\/\/abbingtonhouse.co.uk\/residential-rehab\/medically-supervised-detox\/","title":{"rendered":"Medically Supervised Detox"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-post\" data-elementor-id=\"41719\" class=\"elementor elementor-41719\" data-elementor-post-type=\"residential-rehab\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-57b6bf72 e-flex e-con-boxed cmsmasters-block-default e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"57b6bf72\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-66100e5c cmsmasters-block-default cmsmasters-sticky-default elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"66100e5c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>At Abbington House, we understand that detoxification is often the first and most crucial step in recovery from substance addiction. Our medically supervised detox programme is designed to ensure that this process is as safe, comfortable, and supportive as possible. Detox can be challenging, but with the right care and guidance, it paves the way for successful treatment. Our clinical team, led by experienced professionals, provides round-the-clock medical supervision to manage withdrawal symptoms and minimise discomfort during this stage.<\/p><p>Every client begins with a comprehensive consultation with our Treatment Team, who will gather detailed information about your medical history, psychiatric background, and addiction history. This allows us to tailor a medically assisted detox plan that is specific to your needs. Not every addiction requires detox, but for many substances such as <a href=\"https:\/\/abbingtonhouse.co.uk\/alcohol-rehab\/alcohol-detox\/\">alcohol<\/a>, opioids, and benzodiazepines\u2014it is crucial for safely removing harmful toxins from the body. Our team carefully monitors each client to ensure their safety and well-being throughout the process.<\/p><p>What sets Abbington House apart is our compassionate and holistic approach. Detoxification is only the beginning of your recovery journey. If, after detox, it is assessed by our clinical professionals that a more comprehensive mental health assessment with a substance misuse doctor is needed, we will have this conversation with you and your loved ones to ensure you receive the best possible care. We believe in treating not just the addiction but the person as a whole, ensuring that any underlying mental health issues are addressed.<\/p><p>A comprehensive treatment programme at Abbington House is made up of three stages: detox, addiction therapy, and aftercare. Once detox is completed, clients move into the next phase of their personalised treatment plan, which includes a range of therapies designed to support long-term recovery. We walk with you every step of the way, ensuring you feel safe, supported, and empowered as you begin your journey to healing.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-18668121 cmsmasters-block-default cmsmasters-sticky-default elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"18668121\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Frequently Asked Questions<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-deabd54 cmsmasters-title-alignment-left cmsmasters-item-icon-position-left cmsmasters-trigger-icon-view-default cmsmasters-block-default cmsmasters-sticky-default elementor-widget elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles cmsmasters-widget-toggles\" data-id=\"deabd54\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;toggles&quot;:[{&quot;toggle_title&quot;:&quot;What is medically supervised detox, and why is it necessary?&quot;,&quot;toggle_content&quot;:&quot;&lt;p&gt;The &lt;span style=\\&quot;font-weight: 400;\\&quot;&gt;Medically supervised detox involves managing the withdrawal symptoms that occur when someone stops using substances. It is necessary for many substances to ensure a safe and comfortable detoxification process.&lt;\\\/span&gt;&lt;\\\/p&gt;&quot;,&quot;_id&quot;:&quot;8b62f61&quot;,&quot;content_type&quot;:&quot;toggle-content&quot;,&quot;saved_section&quot;:null,&quot;saved_template&quot;:null,&quot;saved_widget&quot;:null,&quot;item_icon&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;library&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;toggle_custom_id&quot;:&quot;&quot;},{&quot;toggle_title&quot;:&quot;Will I receive a personalised detox plan?&quot;,&quot;toggle_content&quot;:&quot;&lt;p&gt;Yes, after a comprehensive consultation with our Substance Misuse Specialist Doctor, a medically assisted detox plan will be tailored to your specific needs, based on your medical and addiction history.&lt;\\\/p&gt;&quot;,&quot;_id&quot;:&quot;9948ec9&quot;,&quot;content_type&quot;:&quot;toggle-content&quot;,&quot;saved_section&quot;:null,&quot;saved_template&quot;:null,&quot;saved_widget&quot;:null,&quot;item_icon&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;library&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;toggle_custom_id&quot;:&quot;&quot;},{&quot;toggle_title&quot;:&quot;What happens if I need more mental health support after detox?&quot;,&quot;toggle_content&quot;:&quot;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-weight: 400;\\&quot;&gt;If our clinical team assesses that a more comprehensive mental health assessment with a psychiatrist is required after detox, we will discuss the next steps with you and your loved ones to ensure you receive appropriate care.&lt;\\\/span&gt;&lt;\\\/p&gt;&quot;,&quot;_id&quot;:&quot;28bc3e7&quot;,&quot;content_type&quot;:&quot;toggle-content&quot;,&quot;saved_section&quot;:null,&quot;saved_template&quot;:null,&quot;saved_widget&quot;:null,&quot;item_icon&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;library&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;toggle_custom_id&quot;:&quot;&quot;},{&quot;toggle_title&quot;:&quot;How long does the detox process usually take?&quot;,&quot;toggle_content&quot;:&quot;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-weight: 400;\\&quot;&gt;The length of detox varies depending on the substance and individual circumstances, but it typically lasts between 5 and 10 days. During this time, you will receive constant medical supervision and support.&lt;\\\/span&gt;&lt;\\\/p&gt;&quot;,&quot;_id&quot;:&quot;9775964&quot;,&quot;content_type&quot;:&quot;toggle-content&quot;,&quot;saved_section&quot;:null,&quot;saved_template&quot;:null,&quot;saved_widget&quot;:null,&quot;item_icon&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;library&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;toggle_custom_id&quot;:&quot;&quot;},{&quot;_id&quot;:&quot;9d3ef4b&quot;,&quot;toggle_title&quot;:&quot;What happens after detox?&quot;,&quot;toggle_content&quot;:&quot;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;font-weight: 400;\\&quot;&gt;After detox, you will transition into the next stage of your personalised treatment programme, which includes addiction therapy and aftercare to support your long-term recovery.&lt;\\\/span&gt;&lt;\\\/p&gt;&quot;,&quot;content_type&quot;:&quot;toggle-content&quot;,&quot;saved_section&quot;:null,&quot;saved_template&quot;:null,&quot;saved_widget&quot;:null,&quot;item_icon&quot;:{&quot;value&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;library&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;toggle_custom_id&quot;:&quot;&quot;}],&quot;default_toggle&quot;:1,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;toggles&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"cmsmasters-toggles.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__list\" role=\"tablist\"><div class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__item\"><h5 id=\"elementor-tab-title-2331\" class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__title\" data-tab=\"1\" role=\"tab\" aria-controls=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__content-2331\" aria-expanded=\"false\"><a class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__title-link cmsmasters_enable_trigger_icon\" href=\"#\"><span class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__title-text\">What is medically supervised detox, and why is it necessary?<\/span><\/a><span class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__trigger\"><span class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__trigger-closed\"><i aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Closed\" class=\"cmsdemo-icon- cms-demo-icon-dropdown-down\"><\/i><\/span><span class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__trigger-opened\"><i aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Opened\" class=\"cmsdemo-icon- cms-demo-icon-dropdown-up\"><\/i><\/span><\/span><\/h5><div id=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__content-2331\" class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__content elementor-clearfix\" data-tab=\"1\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"elementor-tab-title-2331\"><p>The <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Medically supervised detox involves managing the withdrawal symptoms that occur when someone stops using substances. It is necessary for many substances to ensure a safe and comfortable detoxification process.<\/span><\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__item\"><h5 id=\"elementor-tab-title-2332\" class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__title\" data-tab=\"2\" role=\"tab\" aria-controls=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__content-2332\" aria-expanded=\"false\"><a class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__title-link cmsmasters_enable_trigger_icon\" href=\"#\"><span class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__title-text\">Will I receive a personalised detox plan?<\/span><\/a><span class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__trigger\"><span class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__trigger-closed\"><i aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Closed\" class=\"cmsdemo-icon- cms-demo-icon-dropdown-down\"><\/i><\/span><span class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__trigger-opened\"><i aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Opened\" class=\"cmsdemo-icon- cms-demo-icon-dropdown-up\"><\/i><\/span><\/span><\/h5><div id=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__content-2332\" class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__content elementor-clearfix\" data-tab=\"2\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"elementor-tab-title-2332\"><p>Yes, after a comprehensive consultation with our Substance Misuse Specialist Doctor, a medically assisted detox plan will be tailored to your specific needs, based on your medical and addiction history.<\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__item\"><h5 id=\"elementor-tab-title-2333\" class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__title\" data-tab=\"3\" role=\"tab\" aria-controls=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__content-2333\" aria-expanded=\"false\"><a class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__title-link cmsmasters_enable_trigger_icon\" href=\"#\"><span class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__title-text\">What happens if I need more mental health support after detox?<\/span><\/a><span class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__trigger\"><span class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__trigger-closed\"><i aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Closed\" class=\"cmsdemo-icon- cms-demo-icon-dropdown-down\"><\/i><\/span><span class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__trigger-opened\"><i aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Opened\" class=\"cmsdemo-icon- cms-demo-icon-dropdown-up\"><\/i><\/span><\/span><\/h5><div id=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__content-2333\" class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__content elementor-clearfix\" data-tab=\"3\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"elementor-tab-title-2333\"><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If our clinical team assesses that a more comprehensive mental health assessment with a psychiatrist is required after detox, we will discuss the next steps with you and your loved ones to ensure you receive appropriate care.<\/span><\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__item\"><h5 id=\"elementor-tab-title-2334\" class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__title\" data-tab=\"4\" role=\"tab\" aria-controls=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__content-2334\" aria-expanded=\"false\"><a class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__title-link cmsmasters_enable_trigger_icon\" href=\"#\"><span class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__title-text\">How long does the detox process usually take?<\/span><\/a><span class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__trigger\"><span class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__trigger-closed\"><i aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Closed\" class=\"cmsdemo-icon- cms-demo-icon-dropdown-down\"><\/i><\/span><span class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__trigger-opened\"><i aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Opened\" class=\"cmsdemo-icon- cms-demo-icon-dropdown-up\"><\/i><\/span><\/span><\/h5><div id=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__content-2334\" class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__content elementor-clearfix\" data-tab=\"4\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"elementor-tab-title-2334\"><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The length of detox varies depending on the substance and individual circumstances, but it typically lasts between 5 and 10 days. During this time, you will receive constant medical supervision and support.<\/span><\/p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__item\"><h5 id=\"elementor-tab-title-2335\" class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__title\" data-tab=\"5\" role=\"tab\" aria-controls=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__content-2335\" aria-expanded=\"false\"><a class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__title-link cmsmasters_enable_trigger_icon\" href=\"#\"><span class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__title-text\">What happens after detox?<\/span><\/a><span class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__trigger\"><span class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__trigger-closed\"><i aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Closed\" class=\"cmsdemo-icon- cms-demo-icon-dropdown-down\"><\/i><\/span><span class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__trigger-opened\"><i aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-label=\"Opened\" class=\"cmsdemo-icon- cms-demo-icon-dropdown-up\"><\/i><\/span><\/span><\/h5><div id=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__content-2335\" class=\"elementor-widget-cmsmasters-toggles__content elementor-clearfix\" data-tab=\"5\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"elementor-tab-title-2335\"><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">After detox, you will transition into the next stage of your personalised treatment programme, which includes addiction therapy and aftercare to support your long-term recovery.<\/span><\/p><\/div><\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>At Abbington House, we understand that detoxification is often the first and most crucial step in recovery from substance addiction. Our medically supervised detox programme is designed to ensure that this process is as safe, comfortable, and supportive as possible. Detox can be challenging, but with the right care and guidance, it paves the way&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":41610,"template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"inline_featured_image":false},"class_list":["post-41719","residential-rehab","type-residential-rehab","status-publish","has-post-thumbnail","hentry"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/abbingtonhouse.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/residential-rehab\/41719","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/a